oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Frazier Moss - fiddle tunes and interviews
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Recordings of various fiddle tunes, as performed by Frazier Moss (performer) and Eddie Young (performer) with guitar accompaniment. Recording also contains an interview with Frazier Moss, conducted by Mark Schatz.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Frazier Moss; Eddie Young
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dcterms:tableOfContents: Test tone -- Anniversary (Frazier Moss, Eddie Young) -- Westfalia Waltz (Frazier Moss, Eddie Young) -- The Skaters Waltz (Frazier Moss, Eddie Young) -- Yellow Rose Waltz (Frazier Moss, Eddie Young) -- Birth Of The Blues (Frazier Moss, Eddie Young) -- Faded Love (Frazier Moss, Eddie Young) -- Twilight Waltz (Frazier Moss, Eddie Young) -- Melody Of Love (Frazier Moss, Eddie Young) -- Capri Waltz (Frazier Moss, Eddie Young) -- Tennessee Polka (Frazier Moss, Eddie Young) -- Frazier Moss and Eddie Young talk -- Mark Schatz and Frazier Moss interview -- Moss talks about meeting Eddie Young -- Moss talks about how he started his career in music -- Moss talks about all the different players he has met and played with -- Moss talks about his relationship with Dottie West -- Moss talks about Bob Douglas -- Moss talks (incomplete)
